      "Respect slot limits exactly.",
      "Keep headings short and meaningful.",
      "Keep body text concise enough for premium report slides.",
      "Do not invent extra cards, rows, bullets or labels.",
      "Use slide-ready business phrasing rather than essay-style prose."
